text.__SUMMARY__: Solanum ovum-fringillae is a species of plant in the family Solanaceae. It is endemic to Brazil.
text.Sources: Bohs, L. (1998). "Solanum ovum-fringillae". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T35474A9934576. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T35474A9934576.en. Retrieved 15 January 2018.
